{"tid":397510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[賽跑冠軍系列] 過路男深水埗遭的士撞斃 街坊目擊有人衝燈","createTime":"2017-09-12T14:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T02:52:20.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca7ba2ee55d4ad2b573b5406a200270c6346be97","tid":397510,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:02:16.000Z","msg":"<strong>過路男深水埗遭的士撞斃 街坊目擊有人衝燈</strong><br />\n<br />\n即時突發  2017-09-12 21:09:59 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n晚上7時許，一名中年男途人在深水埗南昌街紅綠燈位，向荔枝角道方向過路時，遭一輛的士撞到，重傷昏迷倒地。救護員接報趕至，把他送院救治，惜終告不治。<br />\n<br />\n有目擊街坊指，事發時行人燈號亮起紅燈，疑有人不依交通燈號，衝燈過路肇禍。涉事的士右邊車頭燈損毀，馬路上遺下血迹及男傷者的一對鞋。現場附近有商店設有閉路電視，警方事後翻查片段，並把的士司機帶上警車調查。<br />\n<br />\n你敢爆，我敢獎！ 即Call《蘋果》24小時爆相爆片熱線 ：63836568"},{"pid":"e410414212c3f30fcd8700a496b5390b0160334a","tid":397510,"uid":130394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T15:05:07.000Z","msg":"我賽跑冠軍嚟㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁就跑撚左上天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66e8a91e0e9c53d7a4d4ec990621a55aa3b27cc","tid":397510,"uid":130394,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T15:05:43.000Z","msg":"i am the fastest man <del>alive</del>"},{"pid":"d27e7305804ec911a43c9de29a6bf4309ccf3f37","tid":397510,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T15:12:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09ee6e6e745053f5c6e26114fdfdd03ef265196e","tid":397510,"uid":144466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T15:16:02.000Z","msg":"廢中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249c85c967f9a1a9c1b1ab4b71aff89e09714e0d","tid":397510,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T15:18:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d94fa330dd7f32cfe0f04934f9e5fb4a7c6